name interchar
category Package
revision 77682
shortdesc Managing character class schemes in XeTeX
longdesc The package manages character class schemes of XeTeX. Using
longdesc this package, you may switch among different character class
longdesc schemes. Migration commands are provided for make packages
longdesc using this mechanism compatible with each others.
